    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I came across this question myself recently. Found most of the answers obsolete or unsatisfactory so I created my own:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/UrBPIoED.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/UrBPIoED.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p>It is fully localized and available as part of the Sierra project on GitHub:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/HTTP-RPC/Sierra\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://github.com/HTTP-RPC/Sierra</a></p>\n<p>A time picker is also available:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/cwd5CAWg.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/cwd5CAWg.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
